# VER-016: Perspective Road Z-Test (INDEXED8_2X2)
# 
# Four-triangle road (2 quads) stretching into the distance.
# 64x64 apparent INDEXED8_2X2 texture: 4x4 grid of 16x16 squares,
# index 0 = white, index 1 = black (uniform per-entry).
# Road split into strips to keep V within Q4.12 range (max 4.0).
# Phase 'zclear':    initialise Z-buffer to 0x0000 (reverse-Z far)
# Phase 'palette':   stage palette + index array, trigger PALETTE0
# Phase 'setup':     configure texture and render mode
# Phase 'triangles': submit road strips (MVP-transformed)

